      <title>人工智能热潮席卷 Lumen Technologies，股价创月度新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/lumen-technologies-shares-soar-to-best-month-ever-amid-ai-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人工智能交易和空头回补引发了 Lumen Technologies Inc. 股价在多年恶性抛售之后的疯狂上涨，7 月份 Lumen Technologies Inc. 股价飙升 150%，创下有史以来最佳月度涨幅。]]></description>
